  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At level 7, you revel in the fear of your enemies, using it to fuel your relentless pursuit, turning fear into utter despair.<br />As a bonus action, instead of walking, you can teleport behind a hostile creature within your movement speed range that you can see. This teleportation provokes attacks of opportunity as normal.<br />The target must make a Wisdom saving throw against your highest DC. On a failure, they gain 1 rank of Hopeless.<br />You ignore resistance in applying hopeless ranks and treat immunity as resistance.<br />As a bonus action, you can convert any ranks of Fear that you personally inflicted into ranks of Hopeless.<br />You cannot do this twice or more to the same creature in the same round.</p>",
